&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Important Note&lt;/strong&gt;: Nginx shows limited performance and compatibility on Windows environments, so it&amp;rsquo;s strongly recommended to use &lt;strong&gt;Linux/Unix systems&lt;/strong&gt; in production!&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>